 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
10. the fan of metal is between the fan of indie and the person who growsdaffodil##2
11. the fan of disco is the person who growsbegonia##1
12. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of reggae##1
13. the fan of pop is between the person who growsdaffodil and the fan of reggae##2
